-- Merkel to make statement on Hypo Real: government source
-- 
-- Sun Oct 5, 2008 11:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/05/us-hyporealestate-merkel-idUSTRE49410S20081005

 

 BERLIN  (Reuters) - German Chancellor Angela Merkel will make a statement on the financial crisis and the plight of lender Hypo Real Estate on Sunday afternoon, a government source said. 

 Officials from the German government, central bank and financial regulator were meeting on Sunday in an effort to save the bank after a Berlin-brokered deal to rescue it unraveled. (Reporting by Hans-Edzard Busemann, writing by Iain Rogers)